## File Structure

```
src/
  core/           # BaseEscrow, DisputeEscrow, TradeInfraEscrow
  interfaces/     # ITradeOracle, IReceivableMinter
  libraries/      # EscrowTypes, ReputationLibrary
  governance/     # ProtocolArbiterMultisig
  CredenceReceivable.sol
  CentralizedTradeOracle.sol
  ChainlinkTradeOracle.sol

test/             # Foundry tests (13 test suites, 300+ tests)
script/           # Deployment scripts
web/              # Next.js frontend
  src/
    app/          # pages (dashboard, escrow/[id], disputes, receivables, admin)
    components/  # React components
    hooks/        # wagmi hooks
    lib/          # ABIs, config
    types/        # TypeScript types
```

